OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start across the area
OL,6,Fwith mist in places. Away from the
OL,7,Fcoast, cloud breaks rapidly leading to
OL,8,Fa sunny and dry day for most. Light
OL,9,Fnortherly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening across
OL,12,Fthe region. Cloud develops from the
OL,13,Fnortheast for many areas overnight
OL,14,Fwith patchy drizzle around the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FCloudy for much of the
OL,17,Fregion with some patchy drizzle at
OL,18,Ftimes, particularly for coastal areas.
OL,19,FCooler than recent days. Light
OL,20,Fnortherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
